Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要取回曾經失去的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必會比最初更困難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我更加堅定了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應援再次挑戰夢想的島田真夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//NEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真夢夢真是一個充滿謎團的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍藍你是她的好朋友應該知道不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道 不過那個我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身上痣的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好瘋狂…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 「是天國還是地獄？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//NEXT-END
